description: This file defines the interface for the CellularManager message bus component in a C project. It includes function declarations for initialization, finalization, bus checking, and resource freeing, along with relevant macros and include directives.

methods.name: CellularMgr_MessageBus_Init
methods.description: Initializes the message bus with component ID, configuration file, and path.

methods.name: CellularMgr_Mbi_Initialize
methods.description: Performs additional initialization of the message bus module with user data.

methods.name: CellularMgr_Mbi_Finalize
methods.description: Finalizes and cleans up resources for the message bus module.

methods.name: CellularMgr_Mbi_BusCheck
methods.description: Checks the status of the message bus.

methods.name: CellularMgr_Mbi_FreeResources
methods.description: Frees resources with specified priority and user data.
